cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.DS 

This paper deals with feedback control over erasure channels, which is a topic related to control systems (cs.SY) and information theory (cs.IT). The use of sparsity-promoting optimizations is a technique commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and signal processing (cs.DS). Finally, the paper also discusses the issue of stability, which is a concern in networked control systems (cs.NI).
